{"tid":2328773,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘋果A1: 中共起訴10港人　兩未成年者不公開聽證　 律師料聖誕審理　家屬冀深圳旁聽","createTime":"2020-12-16T18:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T09:33:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e7889f26b1783f278bd6a1f5571a906ca57614fa","tid":2328773,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T18:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/131687283_10159700103482448_4782477385020760809_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=GGsvdUG6S3sAX9jaBN5&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=6c8b03c3ff2b5fceb96fa1f8545e09ff&amp;oe=6001B586\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F131687283_10159700103482448_4782477385020760809_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DGGsvdUG6S3sAX9jaBN5%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D6c8b03c3ff2b5fceb96fa1f8545e09ff%26oe%3D6001B586&h=ee97ac0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12港人涉偷渡被扣留在內地接近四個月，深圳市鹽田區檢察院昨發出公告，正式起訴當中10人；另外兩名未成年人則會由檢察院舉行「不公開聽證」。有律師估計當局很可能酌情不起訴兩人，同時偷渡案或「按慣例」在聖誕新年假期審理；家屬則表示希望可以到深圳聽審，促內地盡快公佈審訊時間，並進行公開審訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/572C2DRA6BFLDKRHOC7DMPTCDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2F572C2DRA6BFLDKRHOC7DMPTCDM%2F&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE18RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=8dc00a9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2F572C2DRA6BFLDKRHOC7DMPTCDM%2F&h=883b166d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/572C2DRA6BFLDKRHOC7DMPTCDM/</a>"},{"pid":"58494b20c2ee872a37bf4ed1fa7ad7009568fa6d","tid":2328773,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T18:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eccd8585ef95351847684728a335b0514c583b7f","tid":2328773,"uid":264326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T18:24:05.000Z","msg":"上左去仲落到黎...？"},{"pid":"8335d956e1cfa88c8aade252435e7c690a941270","tid":2328773,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T18:24:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>有不願具名的家屬委託律師指出，檢察院舉行聽證比較少見，既然12人不是同時移送法院起訴，而是有兩人另行聽證，很可能是兩名未成年當事人認罪認罰，然後檢察院酌情不起訴。他稱雖然聽證會是不公開進行，當局亦要通知家屬舉行的日期。</strong>"},{"pid":"c9c755c5395cc60dcc0fb22884465ff9ce1945d9","tid":2328773,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T18:25:40.000Z","msg":"12港人案中兩名未成年港人廖子文及黃臨福，人民檢察院指將擇日舉行不公開聽證。有內地律師指，內地刑事案沒有聽證程序，有關做法是最高人民檢察院（最高檢）作的規定，「是最高檢的所謂創新，自己規定的程序」。有份協助12港人家屬的香港大律師兼支聯會副主席鄒幸彤指，據她對內地處理案件的理解，若以不公開聽證處理，即有機會不作起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/3XIXYYFCJZH2DHCBVOYKO6XDCE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2F3XIXYYFCJZH2DHCBVOYKO6XDCE%2F&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE18RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=9a026b22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2F3XIXYYFCJZH2DHCBVOYKO6XDCE%2F&h=ddc91a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/3XIXYYFCJZH2DHCBVOYKO6XDCE/</a>"},{"pid":"80c33120e64dda32534cdd237400714448586978","tid":2328773,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T18:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2020b1fd36569c580abe768639aded28a4b655","tid":2328773,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T18:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img